                        "text": "A Sallowdrudge uses their net to Grapple a Medium or smaller creature within 30 feet. On a success, the target is grabbed until it Escapes (DC 16) or until an adjacent creature Interacts to remove the net. On a critical hit, the target is restrained rather than grabbed. The Sallowdrudge can't use Entangling Net again until they take 1 minute to refold their net."
